---
title: SuperQuick Italian Sausage and Couscous Soup with Roasted Pepper Pesto and Parmesan
description: Full of comforting and nourishing Italian flavours, this hearty sausage-and-pearl couscous soup is a cozy meal perfect for the whole family. Full of veggies and finished with a sprinkle of Parmesan, it's everything you want on a chilly autumn night.

